text: Daniella Nicole Pineda (born 20 February 1987) is an American actress, writer, and comedian. She was born in Oakland, California. She is known for her role as Zia Rodriguez in Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom. She also starred as Sophie in the television series The Originals. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Oakland, California Category:Comedians from Oakland, California Category:Writers from California
